# ruas_rio_areas_operacao_forca

Description:
Data set ruas_rio enriched with areas_operacao_forca via geographical match.

Primary key:
cod_trecho 

Columns:
- cod_trecho - street segment identifier - string
- nome_completo - complete name of street - string
- bairro - neighborhood - string
- areas_operacao - name of area operacao forca corresponding with cod_trecho